00:00:06.761 --> 00:00:11.572
Today we will prepare Papaya Shake which is also known as Papaya Smoothie.

00:00:12.210 --> 00:00:22.049
Papaya is a very beneficial fruit, easily digestible and is advised for those with digestion problems.

00:00:22.568 --> 00:00:33.762
Papaya large amounts of contains vitamin A, vitamin K, vitamin E, potassium and fibre.

00:00:34.433 --> 00:00:41.374
Papaya should be had by all, but some people don't like it as well as children.

00:00:41.924 --> 00:00:46.967
In this case prepare Papaya Shake and everyone will drink it fondly.

00:00:47.248 --> 00:00:50.684
Let us begin making Papaya Shake.

00:00:51.037 --> 00:00:52.957
The ingredients required

00:00:54.001 --> 00:01:00.624
Pieces of papaya - 1 cup

00:01:01.255 --> 00:01:03.803
Ice cubes - 1 cup

00:01:04.082 --> 00:01:10.943
Cardamom - 2 (optional)

00:01:11.345 --> 00:01:13.678
Sugar - 4 tsp

00:01:13.990 --> 00:01:15.395
Milk - 1 cup

00:01:22.443 --> 00:01:42.842
Put papaya, sugar and halk of milk in mixer.

00:01:54.946 --> 00:02:13.360
Papaya has turned into a smooth and Now add the remaining milk and ice cubes and mix.

00:02:19.313 --> 00:02:22.178
Papaya shake is ready to serve.

00:02:30.381 --> 00:02:37.590
Garnish with cardamom powder.

00:02:37.999 --> 00:02:39.832
Papaya shake is ready.

00:02:43.799 --> 00:02:50.207
